Description: Reverend Pete Anderson - Satin Trans Blue Condition: This Pete Anderson 10th Anniversary is in excellent condition! Serial Number: 30588 Weight: 7 lbs The Pete Anderson PA-1 10th Anniversary guitar celebrates ten years since Reverend launched the Pete Anderson PA-1 Signature, featuring an innovative Uni-Brace system and spruce top. The 10th Anniversary PA-1 is souped up with dog-eared P90s (in Satin Natural with black metal pickup covers, or Satin Trans Blue with nickel pickup covers.)
